text: Robert P. Hollenbeck Sr. (November 5, 1931 â€“ September 5, 2021) was an American Democratic Party politician. He was a member of the New Jersey General Assembly from 1974 until 1986. Hollenbeck was born in Carlstadt, New Jersey. He was a member of the Democratic Party. Hollenbeck died on September 5, 2021 in Barnegat Township, New Jersey at the age of 89. ==References== Category:1931 births Category:2021 deaths Category:State legislators of the United States Category:Politicians from New Jersey Category:Democratic Party (United States) politicians
